{"tid":2330103,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美心大埔西餅廠兩名員工確診及一名員工初步確診","createTime":"2020-12-17T17:17:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T00:39:22.000Z","uid":237283,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a7e43b9d6c3bde898806e11e1a928427e036bacc","tid":2330103,"uid":237283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T17:17:41.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美心集團西餅廠，有三名員工確診及初步確診。<br />\n<br />\n美心集團指，大埔西餅廠有兩名員工確診及一名員工初步確診，三人都在獨立生產區工作。其中一名確診員工有家屬確診須送往檢疫，員工上周二最後一日上班；另一名確診員工上周六最後一日上班。<br />\n<br />\n美心指，在發現有員工確診後已安排患者全組同事，共40人停工及接受病毒檢測，全部呈陰性，相關生產區的產品將暫停生產及供應。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=417002\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417002&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrSL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=c223b8b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417002&h=3ce4cd19\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=417002</a>"},{"pid":"43590ed2deca80f30c07889eb286b1067fa4033f","tid":2330103,"uid":349498,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T17:19:20.000Z","msg":"中黎中去都係藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c11d2e7ae548a196c7c4ded36cdd6c569b34d8","tid":2330103,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T17:23:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a89d9686f7a464542d883908f1b64a0e31907f","tid":2330103,"uid":254165,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"43590ed2deca80f30c07889eb286b1067fa4033f","tid":2330103,"uid":349498,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,